                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-215-off1277 t18320405-215-crimeloc1280"></join>. On the 20th of February I was going up the shop, and caught a glance of the prisoner going out of the shop; I went out, and found him within twenty yards of the door, with these boots, which hung by the side of the counter.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>

               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Two boys who were running threw the boots down; I took them up.</p>
